<td class="" style=""><span class="nickname">Maximilian Karl Emil Weber</span><br />
<span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1864-04-21</span>)</span>21 April 1864<br />
<span class="birthplace"><a href="Erfurt" title="Erfurt">Erfurt</a>, <a href="Province_of_Saxony" title="Province of Saxony">Saxony</a>, <a href="Kingdom_of_Prussia" title="Kingdom of Prussia">Kingdom of Prussia</a></span></td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
